Replicaset
============
A replicaset is a kubernetes workload.
Purpose of replicaset is to mantain stable set of pods.

Deployment ----->manage------> Replicaset -------->manage--------> pods(set of pods)

1.Selector is used to identify the pods it wants to manage.
2.Replica count tells how many pods it can manage.

Replicaset use the pod templates rto create the pods.

